  author =       "Andrew Csinger",
  abstract =     "This document is a review of the literature of three
                 related areas: psychophysical vision research,
                 automatic display generation, and multi-dimensional
                 data visualization. Common threads are explored, and a
                 model of the visualization process is proposed which
                 integrates aspects of these three areas. In the review
                 of psychophysics, attempts to find a set of primitive
                 perceptual channels are explored. In the literature on
                 automatic generation and visualization, attempts to
                 employ these psychophysical findings are investigated.
                 Finally, the proposed model is a framework which might
                 facilitate this kind of cooperation.",
